<a name="index"><hr><br>


<br clear=left><br><br>

<b><li><a href="../index_oc/recent.html#subversive">The Subversive Eye</a></b><br>
No other medium has the ability to enthral, excite, disturb and terrify its audience as does cinema.  This issue of <b>INDEX</b> looks at film censorship around the world and the controversies - over sex, violence, religion and politics - that the silver screen has sparked.</b><br>
