<b><li>Chldren's Rights</b><br>
A range of leaflets/posters and publications to help you explore children's rights. To order any of these publications <a href="../scf/ordera.html">click here.</a> <br><br><br>

<b><li>Children's Rights in the UK</b><br>

There is a growing recognition that children have rights which is
reflected in domestic legislation and international convention. 
This leaflet provides an introduction to children's rights and
the issues raised by this sometimes controversial subject.<br>
<i>'I believe that we should claim certain rights for children and
labour for their universal recognition.' </i> Eglantyne Jebb 1923 (founder of Save the Children). <br>
