education, culture, expression.<br>
<b>*It's our right:</b> The provision articles: rights of care, food,
water, health.<br>
<b>*Keep us safe:</b>  The protection articles:  rights against: neglect,
abuse, exploitation, violence.<br>
<b>*Teachers' handbook: </b> provides the full text of the Convention on
the Rights of the Child, together with a brief history of
children's rights, a description of  the work of Save the
Children and UNICEF-UK and applications of the materials for
subjects and themes in the National Curriculum of England and
