<b><li>Sexual Feelings & Relationships</b><br>
<i>"Sharing yourself with someone you love and respect was really good"</i><br>
This sensitive new booklet examines many of the physical and emotional aspects of sexual feeling and addresses the problems and new feelings young adults experience in relationships. Mainly for those aged 14-16.<p><br>

<b><li>AIDS & HIV Infection - A Guide For Adults</b><br>
Examining many areas of concern, this booklet offers practical advice and information.<p><br>



