The Chief Prosecutor of the World People's Court wrestles with some personal
demons.<p>

<li><b>Tansu &Ccedil;iller</b> <BR>
Turkey's Margaret Thatcher is chic and Westernized - and the hammer
of the Kurds. Kurdish prisoner Leyla Zana is lead witness.<p>

